WEBVTT

00:00:01.130 --> 00:00:02.663
In 2019,

00:00:02.697 --> 00:00:04.630
the highest paid athlete in the world

00:00:04.630 --> 00:00:07.797
was an Argentine footballer
named Lionel Messi.

00:00:08.130 --> 00:00:09.530
And his talent?

00:00:09.563 --> 00:00:12.597
Dribbling a ball down a pitch
and booting it past a goalkeeper.

00:00:13.130 --> 00:00:16.930
It's a skill so revered by fans
and corporate sponsors alike,

00:00:16.963 --> 00:00:18.430
that in 2019,

00:00:18.430 --> 00:00:21.597
Messi took home 104 million dollars.

00:00:21.630 --> 00:00:26.530
That's almost two million dollars
for every goal he scored in season.

00:00:26.530 --> 00:00:30.030
He's a pretty spectacular athlete
by any standard.